The paper discusses information retrieval techniques and citation analysis, which are commonly used in the field of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and machine learning algorithms (cs.DL) to analyze citation contexts. Additionally, the paper discusses the application of this technique to various types of documents, including legal documents (cs.CY) and scientific papers (cs.SI).
